\c 7
\s Inzalo kaIsakari
\p
\v 1 Lemadodaneni kaIsakari: OThola, loPhuwa, uJashubi, loShimroni; bebane\x + Gen. 46.13.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo amadodana kaThola: OUzi, loRefaya, loJeriyeli, loJahimayi, loIbisamu, loShemuweli, izinhloko zendlu yaboyise\x + 6.33.\x*, abakoThola, amaqhawe alamandla ezizukulwaneni zabo; inani labo ensukwini zikaDavida laliyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamakhulu ayisithupha\x + 27.1,24. 7.4,5,7,9,11,40. 2 Sam. 24.1,2,9.\x*.
\v 3 Lamadodana kaUzi: UIzrahiya. Lamadodana kaIzrahiya: OMikayeli, loObhadiya, loJoweli, uIshiya, bebahlanu; beyizinhloko bonke.
\v 4 Kanye labo-ke, ngensendo zabo, ngendlu yaboyise, kwakukhona amaviyo ebutho lempi, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lesithupha, ngoba babelabafazi labantwana abanengi.
\v 5 Labafowabo, phakathi kwensendo zonke zakoIsakari, amaqhawe alamandla, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lesikhombisa, bebhalwe bonke ngezizukulwana.
\s Inzalo kaBhenjamini
\p
\v 6 \add Amadodana\add* kaBhenjamini: OBhela, loBekeri loJediyayeli, bebathathu\x + 8.1. Gen. 46.21. Nani 26.38.\x*.
\v 7 Lamadodana kaBhela: OEziboni, loUzi, loUziyeli, loJerimothi, loIri, bebahlanu; izinhloko zendlu zaboyise, amaqhawe alamandla; bebhalwe ngezizukulwana, babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamatshumi amathathu lane.
\v 8 Njalo amadodana kaBekeri: OZemira, loJowashi, loEliyezeri, loEliyohenayi, loOmri, loJeremothi, loAbhiya, loAnathothi\x + 6.60.\x*, loAlemethi\x + 6.60.\x*; bonke laba babengamadodana kaBekeri.
\v 9 Bebhalwe ngensendo ngezizukulwana zabo, izinhloko zezindlu zaboyise, amaqhawe alamandla, babezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lamakhulu amabili.
\v 10 Njalo amadodana kaJediyayeli: UBilihani. Lamadodana kaBilihani: OJewushi, loBhenjamini, loEhudi, loKenahana, loZethani, loTarshishi, loAhishahari.
\v 11 Bonke laba babengamadodana kaJediyayeli, ngezinhloko zaboyise, amaqhawe alamandla; babeyizinkulungwane ezilitshumi lesikhombisa lamakhulu amabili, angaphuma ebuthweni ukuya empini.
\v 12 LoShupimi loHupimi babengamadodana kaIri, \add lo\add*Hushimi amadodana kaAheri.
\s Inzalo kaNafithali
\p
\v 13 Amadodana kaNafithali: OJahaziyeli, loGuni, loJezeri, loShaluma, amadodana kaBiliha.
\s Inzalo kaManase
\p
\v 14 Amadodana kaManase\x + Nani 26.29-33.\x*: UAsiriyeli \add umkakhe\add* amzalayo. (Umfazi wakhe omncinyane umAramukazi wazala uMakiri uyise kaGileyadi\x + Josh. 17.1.\x*.
\v 15 UMakiri wathatha udadewabo kaHupimi loShupimi, waba ngumka\add khe\add*, obizo lakhe nguMahaka\x + 7.16.\x*.) Lebizo leyesibili lalinguZelofehadi; njalo uZelofehadi wayelamadodakazi\x + Nani 26.33.\x*.
\v 16 UMahaka umkaMakiri wasezala indodana, wayitha ibizo \add wathi\add* nguPereshi; lebizo lomfowabo lalinguShereshi, lamadodana akhe ayengoUlamu loRakema\x + Gen. 38.4,5.\x*.
\v 17 Njalo amadodana kaUlamu: UBedani\x + 1 Sam. 12.11.\x*. La ayengamadodana kaGileyadi indodana kaMakiri indodana kaManase.
\v 18 Udadewabo uHamolekethi wasezala oIshodi loAbiyezeri loMahla.
\v 19 Lamadodana kaShemida ayengoAhiyani loShekema loLikhi loAniyamu\x + Josh. 17.2.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaEfrayimi
\p
\v 20 Njalo amadodana kaEfrayimi: OShuthela, loBeredi indodana yakhe, loTahathi indodana yakhe, loEleyada indodana yakhe, loTahathi indodana yakhe\x + Nani 26.35.\x*,
\v 21 loZabadi indodana yakhe, loShuthela indodana yakhe, loEzeri loEleyadi, amadoda eGathi azalelwa kulelolizwe abababulalayo, ngoba behlela ukuthatha izifuyo zabo\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*.
\v 22 UEfrayimi uyise walila insuku ezinengi; abafowabo basebesiza uku\add za\add*mduduza.
\v 23 Wasengena kumkakhe; wathatha isisu, wazala indodana; waseyitha ibizo \add wathi\add* nguBeriya, ngoba wayesebubini endlini yakhe.
\v 24 Lendodakazi yakhe yayinguShera, owakha iBethi-Horoni engaphansi lengaphezulu, leUzeni-Shera\x + Josh. 10.10.\x*.
\v 25 Njalo uRefa wayeyindodana yakhe, loReshefi, loTela indodana yakhe, loTahani indodana yakhe,
\v 26 uLadani indodana yakhe, uAmihudi indodana yakhe, uElishama indodana yakhe\x + Nani 1.10. 7.48.\x*,
\v 27 uNoni indodana yakhe, uJoshuwa indodana yakhe\x + Nani 13.16.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Lemfuyo yawo lendawo zawo zokuhlala kwakuyiBhetheli lemizana yayo\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*, langempumalanga iNaharani, langentshonalanga iGezeri lemizana yayo\x + Josh. 16.3.\x*, leShekema lemizana yayo, kwaze kwaba seAya lemizana yayo.
\v 29 Lasemingceleni yabantwana bakoManase\x + Josh. 17.7. Josh. 17.11.\x*, iBeti-Sheyani lemizana yayo, iThahanakhi lemizana yayo, iMegido lemizana yayo, iDori lemizana yayo. Kule kwahlala abantwana bakoJosefa indodana kaIsrayeli.
\s Inzalo kaAsheri
\p
\v 30 Abantwana bakaAsheri: OImina\x + Gen. 46.17. Nani 26.44.\x*, loIshiva\x + Gen. 46.17. Nani 26.44.\x*, loIshivi\x + Gen. 46.17. Nani 26.44.\x*, loBeriya, loSera udadewabo.
\v 31 Njalo amadodana kaBeriya: OHeberi, loMalikiyeli onguyise kaBirizayithi.
\v 32 UHeberi wasezala oJafilethi loShomeri loHothamu loShuwa udadewabo.
\v 33 Lamadodana kaJafilethi: OPasaki loBimihali loAshivathi; la ngamadodana kaJafilethi.
\v 34 Lamadodana kaShemeri: OAhi, loRohiga, uJehuba, loAramu.
\v 35 Njalo amadodana kaHelemu umfowabo: OZofa loImina loSheleshi loAmali.
\v 36 Njalo amadodana kaZofa: OSuwa, loHarineferi, loShuwali, loBeri, loImra,
\v 37 uBezeri, loHodi, loShama, loShilisha, loIthirani\x + 7.38.\x*, loBehera.
\v 38 Njalo amadodana kaJetheri\x + 7.38.\x*: OJefune loPisipa loAra.
\v 39 Njalo amadodana kaUla: OAra loHaniyeli loRiziya.
\v 40 Bonke laba babengabantwana bakaAsheri, izinhloko zendlu yaboyise, abakhethiweyo, amaqhawe alamandla, izinhloko zeziphathamandla. Basebebhalwa ngezizukulwana ebuthweni empini; inani labo lalingamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lesithupha\x + 9.22.\x*.
